    "attributes": {
        "action": "Instant and permanent driving ban for failing a blood alcohol concentration test",
        "additional_details": "If the culprit has been caught by the police, it often won't be their first time offending. Drink driving costs lives. If they're fleeing danger, they can call 999 or call a taxi if they need to travel.",
        "background": "Instant and permanent driving ban for having a blood alcohol concentration test over the legal limit, such as a breathalyser test. There is no excuse for driving under the influence. There should be a one strike and you're out policy.",
